NAME
     imaze - the game of iMaze

SYNOPSIS
     imaze [ -hq ] [ -H  _s_e_r_v_e_r-_h_o_s_t[:_s_e_r_v_e_r-_p_o_r_t] ]  [ -S _s_o_u_n_d-
           _d_i_r_e_c_t_o_r_y ]  [ -j | -J _j_o_y_s_t_i_c_k-_d_e_v_i_c_e ]  [ -D _d_e_v_i_c_e-
           _i_n_d_e_x ]

DESCRIPTION
     imaze is a TCP/IP client with 3D graphics for XView,  Motif,
     and  Athena Widgets for the multi-player network action game
     iMaze.

